  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Providing apprenticeships during the coronavirus (COVID-19) outbreak
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">This document sets out guidance for apprentices, employers, training providers and assessment organisations in response to the impact of coronavirus (COVID-19).</p>

  </div>
</div>

